{
    "name": "Harrow Reader",
    "type": "npc",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Harrow Reader",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "A harrow deck is a set of 54 cards with symbolic illustrations that serves as a sacred divining tool. Feared by the superstitious and avoided by those who know better than to tempt fate, harrow readers live and work in traveling communities, often moving from town to town as opportunities arise. For encounters involving social interaction, the harrow reader is a 3rd-level challenge.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Humanoid</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"14\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Society</a></u>)</b>: DC 13",
            "sources": [
                {
                    "type": "source",
                    "name": "Gamemastery Guide",
                    "link": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "Gamemastery Guide pg. 228",
                        "alt": "Gamemastery Guide pg. 228",
                        "href": "https://paizo.com/products/btq01zq7"
                    },
                    "page": 228
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Mystics",
            "type": "section",
            "sections": [
                {
                    "name": "Dark Rituals",
                    "type": "section",
                    "text": "Most rituals have a simple gp cost and skills. But what if a desperate NPC is willing to offer something darker, such as lives, souls, or worse? Such a nefarious ritual uses a normal ritual as a baseline, but the DCs and proficiency requirements might be reduced or waived entirely, as might any gp cost.",
                    "sources": [
                        {
                            "type": "source",
                            "name": "Gamemastery Guide",
                            "link": {
                                "type": "link",
                                "name": "Gamemastery Guide pg. 228",
                                "alt": "Gamemastery Guide pg. 228",
                                "href": "https://paizo.com/products/btq01zq7"
                            },
                            "page": 228
                        }
                    ],
                    "subtype": "sidebar",
                    "sidebar_type": "advice_and_rules",
                    "sidebar_heading": "Advice and Rules",
                    "image": {
                        "type": "image",
                        "name": "Advice and Rules",
                        "image": "Sidebar_1_AdviceAndRules.png"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "name": "Forms Of Fortune-Telling",
                    "type": "section",
                    "text": "",
                    "sources": [
                        {
                            "type": "source",
                            "name": "Gamemastery Guide",
                            "link": {
                                "type": "link",
                                "name": "Gamemastery Guide pg. 228",
